<li class="gallerybox" style="width: 235px;"><div class="thumb" style="width: 230px; height: 230px;"><figure-inline typeof="mw:Image"><a href="./File:Hokusai_(1828)_Cuckoo_and_Azaleas.jpg"><img resource="./File:Hokusai_(1828)_Cuckoo_and_Azaleas.jpg" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/95/Hokusai_%281828%29_Cuckoo_and_Azaleas.jpg/148px-Hokusai_%281828%29_Cuckoo_and_Azaleas.jpg" data-file-width="750" data-file-height="1014" data-file-type="bitmap" height="200" width="148" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/95/Hokusai_%281828%29_Cuckoo_and_Azaleas.jpg/296px-Hokusai_%281828%29_Cuckoo_and_Azaleas.jpg 2x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/95/Hokusai_%281828%29_Cuckoo_and_Azaleas.jpg/222px-Hokusai_%281828%29_Cuckoo_and_Azaleas.jpg 1.5x"/></a></figure-inline></div><div class="gallerytext"><i>Cuckoo and Azaleas</i>, 1834<br/>from the Small Flower series</div></li>
